===Pronunciation===
[[w:AHD|AHD]]: krā'ŏn, -ən

===Noun===
'''crayon''' (plural: [[crayons]])

# a stick of colored chalk or wax used for drawing

===Verb===
'''to crayon''' ([[crayons]], [[crayoning]], [[crayoned]])

# to draw with a crayon

